            <title>[SOLR-1766] DIH with threads enabled doesn&apos;t respond to the abort command</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-1766</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When the multithreaded entity processor is enabled by adding the threads=&quot;x&quot; attribute to an entity, the thread runner code doesn&apos;t check the status of the abort flag. The process continues to run after the abort command is given.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
